translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster they thought was defeated, barely alive,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance defeated the monster once again.

こんな雑魚も一撃で倒せないとは」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To not be able to defeat such weaklings in one blow."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この辺りの敵はとっても強いですから。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The enemies around here are really strong, after all.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just being able to win alone is amazing."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺以外の誰がするってんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If not me, then who else would do it?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「すごくて強くて素敵な俺様は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I, who am amazing, strong, and wonderful,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「第二の必殺技を使えるようにするぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I’m going to learn to use a second special move.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それまで城には帰れないと思え」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Until then, don’t expect to return to the castle."
